[[Translation:en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Initial interest]]
Sets the initial interest charged on loans for a new map.<br><br>
2 = 2% interest<br>
3 = 3% interest<br>
4 = 4% interest<br>

<pre>
[difficulty]
initial_interest = 2
</pre>

'''Valid options:''' [ 2 | 3 | 4 ]

'''Default:''' 2


